4/4/2017 Við unnum ekkert útaf því ég er að pæla í að fara eftir tímann og
 +fá mér að borða bara veit ekki hvað kannski nautahakk eða eitthvað þannig


6/4/2017 I cry when i shower because the water reminds me of the tears i dropped when i found out i couldn´t love.
But i still remain incapable to feel feelings. just pain. -Matthías
Við ættum að fara vinna matti. -Brynjólfur

25/4/2017 Life is meaningless. I don´t have a purpose here on this planet. I tried loving and caring once.
But that just didn´t work out for me. Because i believe i am a dead man walking on a dangerous road.
The only road i had ever known. -Matthías
ég fékk mer jordan grill í gær og bað um mjög sterkt hann hló af mér og eg eyddi öllum morgninum á dollunni.... -Brynjólfur

26/4/2017 Lenti í vanda með github og gat ekki fundið utur þvi - Brynjólfur

27/4/2017 After all these years of hurting my self and others. I have found out that the wounds heal. But the scars remain the same.
And the scars are what hurt the most. The aftermath is the worst my friend. And most people don´t understand that. -Matthías

2/5/2017 I chose the path. The lonley road. I travel through life alone and scared. Without love and care. No one is there for me
except myself. Life can be meaningless and hurtful. And that´s the way i like it to be. - Matthías
